Below is a curated list of **30 YouTube videos** (3 per expert) prioritized for **actionable insight** on cold outreach, prospecting, and B2B SaaS pipeline building—not view count. Selections draw from verified channel metadata, Gong/Apollo-scale data where available, and frameworks these practitioners actually teach.

---

## 1. Samantha McKenna (#samsales)

**Background:** Former LinkedIn executive; creator of **Show Me You Know Me (SMYKM)**. Reports ~43% open and ~20% reply rates on VIP outreach.

### 1. Show Me You Know Me: Mastering Personalization in Sales Outreach
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IfxqQWdMDYI  
- **Published:** June 18, 2024  
- **Why valuable:** McKenna’s clearest walkthrough of SMYKM—subject lines only the recipient understands, objection preemption, and value framing as problem-solving (not product pitching).  
- **Key lessons:** Subject line + first sentence = preview text; write subject lines meaningless to anyone except the buyer; anticipate objections in email #1; never drop calendar links in first touch; quality over volume (e.g., 20 emails/week).  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** Essential for enterprise/VIP sequences where generic AI emails get ignored; maps directly to account-based outbound for high-ACV deals.

### 2. Show Me You Know Me – Use Data To Personalize Your Outreach
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pzY4QlG-X5A  
- **Published:** June 3, 2023  
- **Why valuable:** Bridges SMYKM philosophy to **operational research** (LinkedIn activity, triggers, Sales Navigator).  
- **Key lessons:** Use posts, comments, and company signals as raw material; tie personalization to the buyer’s current context; trigger-based outreach (funding, hires, launches); build a repeatable research workflow without hours per email.  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** Gives SDR teams a system to feed ABM lists and intent-driven sequences.

### 3. Complete COLD EMAIL COURSE (Apollo Academy)
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H5zsGa9FeuI  
- **Published:** October 23, 2024  
- **Why valuable:** Full free masterclass covering SMYKM end-to-end: research, subject lines, sequences, nurture, and social extensions—her most complete single video.  
- **Key lessons:** “Human, company, space” research model; what SMYKM should/shouldn’t look like; sequence structure when replies don’t come; extend SMYKM beyond email (social, nurture).  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** Use as onboarding curriculum for new AEs/SDRs building a high-touch outbound motion.

