## 4. Kyle Coleman

**Background:** Built outbound at Looker (2→65 SDRs), CMO at Clari/Copy.ai, now Global VP Marketing at ClickUp; advocate of **POV-led outbound** and effectiveness over volume.

### 1. Why Your Outbound Sucks (and How to Fix It) with Kyle Coleman
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g9mejr_-odc  
- **Published:** August 15, 2025  
- **Why valuable:** Coleman’s sharpest POV on **why volume-based outbound fails** and what high-effort, insight-led outreach looks like in practice.  
- **Key lessons:** Research executive priorities before first touch; POV beats personalization theater; phone often wins for senior buyers when paired with real insight; most teams won’t do the hard research— that’s the moat.  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** Strategic reset for SaaS teams drowning in low-reply automated sequences.

### 2. Scaling Your Outbound Engine ft. Kyle Coleman
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y7QLIHx1wpw  
- **Published:** July 16, 2020  
- **Why valuable:** Operator perspective on scaling SDR teams from 1→60+ at Looker ($100K→$100M+ ARR)—still one of his best pipeline-building interviews.  
- **Key lessons:** Outbound strategy must match company stage; empower frontline reps to iterate cadences; cascade “why” from leadership, “how” from reps; continuous feedback loop on what works.  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** Playbook for Series A–C SaaS building their first serious outbound function.

### 3. AI in GTM: Effectiveness Over Efficiency
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GC3Wsg8gu00  
- **Published:** September 9, 2025  
- **Why valuable:** Short but foundational—defines how to use AI in outbound **without destroying inbox trust**.  
- **Key lessons:** Efficiency (volume automation) created inbox disaster; effectiveness = quality AI outputs reps don’t rewrite; train AI on your POV or counterproductive; volume game is over—insight game wins.  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** Guides AI-augmented outbound policy for 2025–2026 SaaS GTM teams.

