## 5. Jason Bay (Outbound Squad)

**Background:** Trains Shopify, Gong, Zoom, Rippling; creator of **Reply Method**, **KISS sequencing**, and Gong-backed email data.

### 1. Outbound Prospecting Masterclass: Everything You Need to Book Meetings in 2026
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dDM80maP1N0  
- **Published:** November 18, 2025  
- **Why valuable:** Full modern outbound playbook: targeting, messaging matrix, multi-channel sequencing, and AI (10-80-10 rule).  
- **Key lessons:** **Martini-glass pipeline** (focus high-relevance accounts); **Messaging Matrix** for offers that earn replies; **KISS sequencing** (multi-day, multi-touch, multi-channel); use AI for research/draft, human for judgment.  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** End-to-end framework for rebuilding a 2026 SaaS outbound program.

### 2. Cold Email Masterclass: Everything You Need To Book Meetings in 2026
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JX1UNIJwcCY  
- **Published:** May 5, 2026  
- **Why valuable:** **Reply Method** in depth, backed by 85M-email Gong analysis.  
- **Key lessons:** Five parts—subject (open only), relevance opener, problem (“why change?”), value + social proof (+40% replies), soft CTA; no product pitch in subject or opener; follow-ups must add new value.  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** Standard operating procedure for SaaS cold email copy and QA.

### 3. Live Cold Calls: How Many Meetings Can The #1 Sales Trainer Book?
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9WtOHUDgbIA  
- **Published:** December 2, 2025  
- **Why valuable:** Bay executes live—permission-based opener, problem hook, close—proving the frameworks under real conditions.  
- **Key lessons:** Intro → hook (problem, not product) → close; list quality (connect rate) matters; warm up via managers before calling CROs; debrief every call.  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** Shows how phone fits into email-first SaaS sequences with real metrics.

