## 7. Alex Berman

**Background:** Built X27/Email10k on cold email at scale; strong on infrastructure and deliverability.

### 1. How to Cold Email Clients (Winning Cold Email Templates)
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hatrtJIncLc  
- **Published:** September 3, 2024  
- **Why valuable:** Current template breakdown with structural rationale—not just swipe files.  
- **Key lessons:** “Forwardable email” test; specificity with numbers; one-sentence value prop; smallest viable CTA; deliverability before copy.  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** Template QA checklist for SaaS outbound teams.

### 2. I Studied 1,000,000 Cold Emails, Here’s What Works in 2025
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4qCXuIQO5T4  
- **Published:** June 30, 2025  
- **Why valuable:** Data-driven patterns from massive send volume—what top 1% do differently.  
- **Key lessons:** Clear outcome per email; tight ICP vs. spray-and-pray; common denominators of high performers; avoid generic blasts.  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** Benchmark your SaaS sequences against empirical patterns.

### 3. The Insane Psychology Behind Cold Email
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8gi8tCb3Q4I  
- **Published:** May 20, 2025  
- **Why valuable:** Focuses on **pre-read decisions** (sender name, subject, preview)—where most campaigns die.  
- **Key lessons:** Thin-slicing in <2 seconds; personal sender name; curiosity-gap subject lines; preview text as second subject line; reciprocity (give value before ask); Tue–Thu mid-morning sends.  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** Optimizes the top of funnel before scaling send volume.

