## 9. Armand Farrokh (30 Minutes to President’s Club)

**Background:** 30MPC co-host; co-author of *Cold Calling Sucks*; Gong 85M-email playbook collaborator.

### 1. [Playbook] Cold Email — Analyzing 85M+ Cold Emails (2025)
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yjOG_QOJgII  
- **Published:** July 24, 2025  
- **Why valuable:** Most **empirically grounded** video in this list—85M emails with Gong + Bay + Farrokh.  
- **Key lessons:** Signal-driven openers 2× reply rates; KISS clusters (problem email + 2 bumps); when to spend 15 min vs. snippet automation; offers beat “book a meeting” CTAs (+28% replies vs. −44% for meeting asks).  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** Data-backed standards for SaaS outbound QA and testing culture.

### 2. Stop Failing at Cold Email in 2025… Teach Your Reps THIS!
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0KSenwLuFiE  
- **Published:** July 24, 2025  
- **Why valuable:** **Leader’s guide** to building a cold email machine—MVC email, onboarding, coaching metrics.  
- **Key lessons:** 1,000 emails → ~3 meetings baseline; minimum viable cold email for the team; teach + reinforce in 1:1s; metrics to tune (reply rate, positive reply rate, meetings/email).  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** For VPs of Sales/Revenue building repeatable outbound at scale.

### 3. How to Write Cold Emails That Get Replies | Problem + Value Framework
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NLASslONNrU  
- **Published:** July 25, 2025  
- **Why valuable:** Compact module on **Problem + Value** formulas (deeper problem, want-but, before/after).  
- **Key lessons:** Avoid product voice and buzzwords; social proof beats solution proof; write like texting a peer; aspiration + obstacle framing for executives.  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** Copy formulas SDRs can use same-day in sequences.

