## 10. Morgan Ingram (AMP / SDR Chronicles)

**Background:** 4× LinkedIn Top Sales Voice; pioneered video prospecting and LinkedIn-first outbound.

### 1. LinkedIn Blueprint — How SDRs Can Book More Meetings
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I-PmhgTQTik  
- **Published:** April 3, 2025  
- **Why valuable:** Complete **LinkedIn-as-pipeline-channel** system—not spam InMails.  
- **Key lessons:** Treat LinkedIn as conversation, not email; filter for 30-day activity; **Alley-Oop play** (message profile viewers); video/voice notes; coordinate with email/phone for familiarity.  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** LinkedIn is where B2B SaaS buyers live—this turns it into a pipeline lever.

### 2. My LinkedIn Outbound Strategy That Books 25+ Meetings a Month
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nUe5IpnleRc  
- **Published:** November 7, 2024  
- **Why valuable:** Full system without scraped lists or heavy automation—**10-30-10 messaging formula**.  
- **Key lessons:** Profile optimization first; targeted list building; 10-30-10 (trigger/priority → value prop → CTA); consistency beats hacks.  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** Replicable LinkedIn motion for individual reps or small teams.

### 3. LIVE Cold Outreach Sequence Tear-Downs
- **URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C4WCOJa5Nwo  
- **Published:** October 14, 2022  
- **Why valuable:** Live critique of **real sequences**—surfaces targeting vs. messaging vs. timing failures.  
- **Key lessons:** Too much “we” language kills replies; pacing matters (8 touches / 14 days example); diagnose root cause before rewriting copy; LinkedIn touches must differ from email.  
- **B2B SaaS relevance:** Run internal sequence reviews using Ingram’s critique framework.

